    <briefdescription>
<para>Firmware info helper class. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The <ref refid="class_fw_info" kindref="compound">FwInfo</ref> parses the OTA update topic JSON string, extract the content and to store it in private string member variables. It provides methods to parse the JSON string, to validate the received file size and checksum and to split an URL into host and filename. Firthermore it provides getter function to retrieve the extracted strings. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
